headline: Regency Centers Announces Tax Information for Regency Centers 2024 Distributions
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Jan. 21, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Regency Centers Corporation (“Regency Centers” or the “Company”) (Nasdaq:REG) today announced the federal income tax treatment of its 2024 distributions to holders of its Common and Preferred stock.
